
cif-db uses Hadoop compression:

wget http://snappy.googlecode.com/files/snappy-1.0.5.tar.gz
configure
make install
svn checkout http://hadoop-snappy.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ hadoop-snappy-read-only
cd hadoop-snappy-read-only
rm -fr target
mvn install



